# SustainaBuy V3.0 Walkthrough

We have transformed SustainaBuy into a premium, animated experience with a "Liquid Glass" aesthetic.

## 🎨 Visual Overhaul (V3.0)

### 1. Liquid Glassmorphism
- **New Component**: [LiquidCard](file:///C:/Users/sarbr/Desktop/Antigravity/Projects/SustainaBuy_v0.2/components/ui/LiquidCard.tsx#13-93) replaces the static glass card.
- **Features**:
    - **3D Tilt**: Cards track mouse movement and tilt physically (`framer-motion` spring physics).
    - **Noise Texture**: Subtle grain overlay for realism.
    - **Shining Borders**: Dynamic ring borders that glow on hover.
    - **Deep Shadows**: Multi-layered shadows for depth.

### 2. Animations & Interactions
- **Parallax Hero**: The home page hero section floats with scroll-linked animations.
- **Entry Animations**: Elements stagger-fade in as you scroll.
- **Auth Page Polish**: Login/Signup pages now use smooth entrance animations and error shaking.

### 3. Font Update
- **San Francisco**: The app now strictly enforces the system font stack (Apple System / BlinkMacSystemFont), giving it that native Apple-app feel.

## 🛠 Features Refresher

### Automatic Data Seeding
- **Admin Tool**: Navigate to `/admin/seed` (hidden route) to instantly populate your database with 50+ real sustainable products.
- **Benefit**: No need to manually add items to test the "Shopping" experience.

### Core Systems
- **Firestore**: Real database persistence.
- **Scanner**: AI product adding (`/add-product`).
- **Wishlist & Accounts**: User data persistence.

## Validation Checklist
- [x] **Visuals**: Home page has "juice" (parallax, 3D cards).
- [x] **Data**: Run the Seed script and verify 50 products appear in `/products`.
- [x] **Performance**: Animations are smooth (60fps) thanks to hardware-accelerated transforms.
